{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"7213","heading":"Amounts available for contract payments","label":"7213 Amounts available for contract payments","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/ch100/schII","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7213","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","References in TextSections 103B, 105B, and 107B of the Agricultural Act of 1949, referred to in subsec. (c)(3), were classified to sections 1444–2, 1444f, and 1445b–3a, respectively, of this title prior to repeal by section 7301(b)(2)(A)–(D) of this title., referred to in subsecs. (e), (f), was repealed by , , .Section 1308(1) of this titlePub. L. 107–171, title I, § 1603(a)116 Stat. 213May 13, 2002"],"amendments":["References in TextSections 103B, 105B, and 107B of the Agricultural Act of 1949, referred to in subsec. (c)(3), were classified to sections 1444–2, 1444f, and 1445b–3a, respectively, of this title prior to repeal by section 7301(b)(2)(A)–(D) of this title., referred to in subsecs. (e), (f), was repealed by , , .Section 1308(1) of this titlePub. L. 107–171, title I, § 1603(a)116 Stat. 213May 13, 2002"],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"Fiscal year amounts","label":"a Fiscal year amounts","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7213%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7213%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"For fiscal year 1996, $5,570,000,000.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7213%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"For fiscal year 1997, $5,385,000,000.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/a/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7213%2Fa%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"For fiscal year 1998, $5,800,000,000.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":null,"label":"4","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/a/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7213%2Fa%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"For fiscal year 1999, $5,603,000,000.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"5","heading":null,"label":"5","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/a/5","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7213%2Fa%2F5","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"For fiscal year 2000, $5,130,000,000.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"6","heading":null,"label":"6","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/a/6","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7213%2Fa%2F6","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"For fiscal year 2001, $4,130,000,000.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"7","heading":null,"label":"7","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/a/7","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7213%2Fa%2F7","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"For fiscal year 2002, $4,008,000,000.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Allocation","label":"b Allocation","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7213%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7213%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"For wheat, 26.26 percent.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7213%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"For corn, 46.22 percent.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/b/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7213%2Fb%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"For grain sorghum, 5.11 percent.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":null,"label":"4","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/b/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7213%2Fb%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"For barley, 2.16 percent.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"5","heading":null,"label":"5","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/b/5","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7213%2Fb%2F5","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"For oats, 0.15 percent.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"6","heading":null,"label":"6","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/b/6","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7213%2Fb%2F6","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"For upland cotton, 11.63 percent.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"7","heading":null,"label":"7","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/b/7","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7213%2Fb%2F7","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"For rice, 8.47 percent.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":"Adjustment","label":"c Adjustment","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7213%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/c/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7213%2Fc%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"adding an amount equal to the sum of all repayments of deficiency payments required under section 114(a)(2) of the Agricultural Act of 1949 () for the commodity;7 U.S.C. 1445j(a)(2)","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/c/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7213%2Fc%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"adding an amount equal to the sum of all refunds of contract payments received during the preceding fiscal year under for the commodity; andsection 7216 of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/c/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7213%2Fc%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"subtracting an amount equal to the amount, if any, necessary during that fiscal year to satisfy payment requirements for the commodity under sections 103B, 105B, or 107B of the Agricultural Act of 1949 for the 1994 and 1995 crop years.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"d","heading":"Additional rice allocation","label":"d Additional rice allocation","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/d","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7213%2Fd","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"In addition to the adjustments required under subsection (c), the amount allocated under subsection (b) for rice contract payments shall be increased by $8,500,000 for each of fiscal years 1997 through 2002.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"e","heading":"Exclusion of certain amounts from contract payments","label":"e Exclusion of certain amounts from contract payments","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/e","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7213%2Fe","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Any amount added pursuant to paragraphs (1) and (2) of subsection (c) to the amount available under subsection (a) for a fiscal year and paid to owners and producers under a contract shall not be treated as a contract payment for purposes of or section 1308(1) of this title. However, the amount of a payment covered by this subsection may not exceed $50,000 per person.section 7215 of this title1See References in text note below.1","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"f","heading":"Effect of payment limitation","label":"f Effect of payment limitation","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213/f","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7213","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7213%2Ff","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The amount available under subsection (a) for a fiscal year shall be reduced by an amount equal to the total amount of contract payments for the fiscal year that owners and producers forgo as a result of operation of the payment limitation under section 1308(1) of this title.1","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}
